<h2>Codex</h2>
<ol>
  <li>You must be a frontend developer and it must be clear that you’re a frontend developer.
  <li>You must answer truthfully whether you <a href=https://www.thesitewizard.com/webdesign/htmlvalidation.shtml>validate your HTML and CSS code</a> (yes! that page! it’s valid!).
  <li>You list your own website. Social media profiles are okay. Organizational and commercial, as well as empty or scammy sites are not okay.
  <li>You acknowledge that there’s no right or entitlement to being or staying linked and listed.
</ol>